Business Brief -- Excel Technology Inc.:
   Definitive Accord Is Signed
   To Buy Quantronix Corp.
Quantronix, based in Hauppauge, N.Y., is a maker of laser
equipment. Excel produces solid-state lasers for scientific
and medical applications.
   Excel traded Friday at $7.375 bid in over-the-counter
trading. Quantronix closed Friday at $2.875, up 12.5 cents,
also in over-the-counter trading.
   Separately, Excel said it exercised about 99% of its
common stock purchase warrants outstanding, which resulted in
proceeds of over $3 million.